data.text/markdown: Butterworth Filter Controls (Independent)

🛠️ Pure Tone + Butterworth Filter

This notebook generates a pure sine tone (choose any piano A), shows its waveform and spectrum, and provides an independent Butterworth low-pass filter you can configure. Use the "Join" cell to apply the filter to the signal (optionally syncing sample rates).
